title: NFL ATL: Return of Win Wess' Toaster; The Mailbag!
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Return of Win Wess' Toaster; The Mailbag!
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal and Chris Wesseling -- gives “ATL Nation” the chance to walk away with Wess’ coveted toaster in the ultimate NFL trivia challenge.  Elsewhere, the gang answers some letters out of the mailbag and picks apart this week’s biggest offseason headlines.
